员丧生，「这是联合国援助人员在如此短的时间内在冲突中丧生人数最多的一次」。 根据联合国近东巴勒斯坦难民救济和工程处发布的数据，自本轮巴以冲突爆发以来，已有 101 名联合国工作人员在加沙地带丧生。痛心！101 人遇难，联合国总部降半旗志哀！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4811dcc99ec58c1babe6147bd77d3160_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "236 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/630125280"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI26Df6qjK9IMvEAMaCTEwMjMwNjM5MCCtocuqBjAAOKsCQAVyCTYzMDEyNTI4MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1699949274.478396", "card_id": "Q_629991021", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 71}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "美国军机在地中海水域坠毁致 5 名士兵死亡，事故原因可能是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "美国军机在地中海水域坠毁致 5 名士兵死亡。 美国欧洲司令部 12 日发表声明说，一架美国军机 10 日在地中海水域发生技术故障并坠毁，造成机上 5 名美军士兵丧生。（此前报道：美军用飞机地中海坠毁） 声明说，事故发生时，该飞机正在进行例行空中加油作业。 美国欧洲司令部 11 日曾发表声明说，美军正在调查事件原因。当时这架飞机执行的「纯粹是与训练相关任务」，没有受到攻击。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-6fed52176a80a60f74555c1ff852613a_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "224 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/629991021"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI26Df6qjK9IMvEAMaCTEwMjI3NjU5NCC4/MWqBjAAOLcBQAZyCTYyOTk5MTAyMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1699949274.480240", "card_id": "Q_629945589", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 183}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果 S13 总决赛是 T1 夺冠，意味着什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "191 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/629945589"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI26Df6qjK9IMvEAMaC